      "properties": {
        "markdown": "# Self-Healing System \u2014 Observability Dashboard\n\n**Pipeline:** `core-service crash` \u2192 `api-service fallback` \u2192 `monitor detects 503` \u2192 `EventBridge event` \u2192 `Lambda restart` \u2192 `recovery-agent docker restart` \u2192 `core-service healthy`\n\n**Namespace:** `SelfHealingSystem` | **Region:** `us-east-1` | **DLQ:** `SelfHealingLambdaDLQ`"
      }
