      "properties": {
        "markdown": "## Phase 7 \u2014 Multi-Service Self-Healing\n\n**Registered services and their strategies:**  `core-service` \u2192 **restart** (fallback: fallback-service)  |  `payment-service` \u2192 **escalate** (critical, no fallback \u2014 operator intervention required)  |  `movie-service` \u2192 **fallback** (routes to fallback-service on CRITICAL)\n\nLambda reads `services_config.json` at init and applies the correct strategy per service automatically."
      }
