        "markdown": "## Strategy Reference\n\n| Service | Strategy | Fallback | Critical |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `core-service` | **restart** | fallback-service | No |\n| `payment-service` | **escalate** | \u2014 | **Yes** |\n| `movie-service` | **fallback** | fallback-service | No |\n\n**restart** \u2014 Recovery-agent restarts the container. Severity ladder: LOW \u2192 MEDIUM \u2192 HIGH \u2192 CRITICAL.\n\n**escalate** \u2014 Minimum severity forced to HIGH on every failure. Operator intervention required. No automatic fallback.\n\n**fallback** \u2014 On CRITICAL, Lambda logs `FALLBACK_AVAILABLE` and recovery-agent routes traffic to `fallback-service`."
